data.title: Full List of Unicode Symbols (◕‿◕) SYMBL
data.meta_description: Unicode web service for character search. Find, copy and paste your favorite characters: 😎 Emoji, ❤ Hearts, 💲 Currencies, → Arrows, ★ Stars and many others 🚩
data.text:
Version: 15.1.0 Release date: September 12, 2023 Total number of characters: 149 813

Almost half a million symbols of all kinds, including arrows, mathematical signs, emojis, hieroglyphics, and ancient scripts, are available. Each symbol lies in its assigned cell in the table. Just scroll down to explore the whole variety of Unicode characters. Or use the block navigation on the right — each character block occupies its range in the table divided into 17 planes. Try 🩒 Chess Symbols for example. Hover over a character you like to see its name or copy it. Click on the symbol name and go to a separate page to study it.
